title: Gorgeous 4/3 Lake home
posting_body: ['REF#: 11249279', 'Gorgeous 4/3 Lake home, 3 levels, exciting & spacious floor plan, 4 bedrooms upstairs + den.', 'Elegant wood stairway with iron railings, wood & tile floors in living areas, laminate floors in bedrooms.', 'Open & bright kitchen w/ granite countertop, kitchen island & SS appliances, updated bathrooms.', 'Cozy paved patio with water fountain, lots of sitting area & lush landscaping, perfect to entertain your guests any time of the year.', 'Premium lot overlooking serene lake.', 'Hurricane accordion shutters throughout the house, newer washer & dryer, Intercom system, water for the lawn taken from lake (lower water bill).', 'This home is in Grand Palms, an established gated Golf Community with 24- hour security, conveniently located close to shopping mall, supermarkets, and easy access to I-75.', 'Lovely!', 'VANESSA REID *|* REALTOR', 'COURTESY OF Canvas Real Estate']
